OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely
OL,6,Fclear initially then mist and low
OL,7,Fcloud is expected to spread westwards.
OL,8,FThere is a chance of a slight frost,
OL,9,Fand patchy fog, for any places that
OL,10,Fremain clear.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FEarly mist, patchy fog or low
OL,13,Fcloud will disperse leaving bright
OL,14,Fconditions as high cloud increases.
OL,15,FChance of an afternoon shower. Rather
OL,16,Fwarm for many places, cooler along the
OL,17,Fcoast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
